	configure.ac: Minor clean-up.

	* am/config_paths.m4 (IU_CONFIG_PATHS):
	Replace obsolete AC_HELP_STRING by AS_HELP_STRING.
	* am/libcurses.m4 (IU_LIB_NCURSES): Likewise.
	* am/readline.m4 (gl_FUNC_READLINE): Likewise.
