	refactored from previous code in do_rlogin().
	(do_rlogin) [WITH_PAM]: Remove variable USER.
	Replace code block by a call to do_pam_check()
	for service `rlogin'.
	(do_shishi_login) [SHISHI && WITH_PAM]:
	Call do_pam_check() for service `krlogin'.

