	* ping/ping6.c: Include <arpa/inet.h>.
	(print_ip_data): New function.
	(print_icmp_error): In verbose mode, let print_ip_data()
	display information on returned packet.

	* ping/ping_echo.c (print_icmp): Use bitwise-and in test.

