	traceroute: Conform to standard application set-up.

	* src/traceroute.c (opt_type): Default to TRACE_UDP.
	(opt_port): Set to TRACE_UDP_PORT.
	(opt_ttl, opt_wait): New variables.
	(argp_options): New options `-f/--first-hop', `-I/--icmp',
