	* configure.ac: Don't check for mkstemp, don't try to replace
	strdup.
	(long long, long double): Remove checks.
	(AM_C_PROTOTYPES): Likewise.
	(AC_FUNC_ALLOCA, AC_FUNC_MALLOC, AC_FUNC_REALLOC): Likewise.

