	size_t to socklen_t.
	* talkd/talkd.c (talkd_run): Change `len' type from size_t to
	socklen_t.
	* tftp/tftp.c (send_file, recvfile): Change `fromlen' type from
	size_t to socklen_t.
	* tftpd/tftpd.c (fromlen): Likewise.
	(main): Change `j' type from size_t to socklen_t.

