	* ifconfig/options.h (parse_opt): Rename to parse_cmdline.
	* ifconfig/system.h (system_argp_child): New extern.
	(system_help_options, SYSTEM_SHORT_OPTIONS)
	(SYSTEM_LONG_OPTIONS): Remove.

