	Julian Gilbey <jdg@debian.org>.

2003-08-29  Marcus Brinkmann  <marcus@gnu.org>

	* syslogd/syslogd.c (init): Use strchr instead memchr.  Skip
	whitespace at the beginning of the next part of a continued line.

