	* ftpd/Makefile.am (INCLUDES): Added $(PATHDEF_FTPDPID)
	* paths: add PATHDEF_FTPDPID

2000-07-07 Alain Magloire

	* glob/Makefile.am: EXTRA_DIST add configure.bat and SMakefile

