	* ftp/cmds.c/sethash(): read the optionnal argument for hash.
	* ftp/ftp.1: update man page, hash take optional argument.
	* ftp/ftp.c/sendrequests(): print hasbyte.
	* ftp/ftp_var.h: hashbytes global var: number of bytes per #
	printed.

